    },
    {
      "text": "Super Strike Eagle is a 1993 combat flight simulation video game for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It was later released in Japan as F-15 Super Strike Eagle (Ｆ－１５スーパーストライクイーグル, F-15 Sūpā Sutoraiku Īguru).\nThe game involves flying airplanes that tests the player's Sidewinder missile and machine gun firing skills against various non-aligned nations that were historically notorious for housing extremist leaders during the Cold War. The game was released in North America, Europe, and Japan approximately simultaneously. In the Japanese version, real political flags are not used unlike the North American version.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super Strike Eagle è un videogioco di genere simulatore di volo militare moderno, pubblicato dalla MicroProse nel 1993 per Super Nintendo Entertainment System. Si pilota un McDonnell Douglas F-15E Strike Eagle in missione in varie zone del mondo.\nÈ l'ultimo titolo della serie di F-15 Strike Eagle, dopo F-15 Strike Eagle III, e l'unico uscito per SNES.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super Strike Eagle, conhecido no Japão como F-15 Super Strike Eagle (Ｆ－１５スーパーストライクイーグル, F-15 Supa Sutoraiku Iguru), é um jogo lançado originalmente para o console Super Nintendo Entertainment System. Nele, pode-se pilotar o caça F-15, em missões da ONU em diversos países do mundo, durante o período da Guerra Fria. Possui um gráfico que o destaca dos demais jogos do mesmo console.",
      "lang": "pt",
      "source": "wikipedia_pt"
    },
    {
      "text": "『スーパー・ストライク・イーグル』は、スーパーファミコン用（SNES）の1993年発売の戦闘フライトシミュレーションビデオゲームです。日本国内では『F-15スーパーストライクイーグル』というタイトルで発売されました。\n\n本作では、プレイヤーが戦闘機を操縦し、サイドワインダーミサイルや機関銃の射撃スキルを試すゲームとなっており、冷戦時代に過激派指導者を抱えることで悪名高い非同盟諸国を相手に戦います。このゲームは、北米、ヨーロッパ、そして日本でほぼ同時期に発売されました。なお、日本版では、北米版とは異なり、実際の政治的な国旗は使用されていません。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
